         <div type="bibliography">
            <listBibl type="secondary">
               <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/KRCWARVB"><seg type="encyclopediaArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Lusini2005EAEDersanaRufael"/><title level="a">Dǝrsanä Rufaʾel</title><title type="short">EAe</title><title level="m">Encyclopaedia Aethiopica</title><author><forename>Gianfrancesco</forename><surname>Lusini</surname></author><editor><forename>Siegbert</forename><surname>Uhlig</surname></editor><pubPlace>Wiesbaden</pubPlace><publisher>Harrassowitz Verlag</publisher><date>2005</date><biblScope unit="volume">II</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">141a</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Lusini2005EAEDersanaRufael</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Lusini2005EAEDersanaRufael</note></bibl>
            </listBibl>
            
            <div type="edition">       
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT7214HomilyJCRuf">
                  <label>Homily by John Chrysostom on the archangel Raphael</label>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Miracles">
                  <label>First collection of miracles of the archangel Raphael</label>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="MiracleImage">
                     <label>On creating a large image of Raphael</label>
                     <note>
                        The following incipit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet130">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 130</ref> according to <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/QZH8VYBF"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/><title level="m">Bybliothecae apostolicae Vaticanae codices manu scripti recensiti iussu Pii XI Pontificis maximi. Codices Aethiopici Vaticani et Borgiani, Barberinianus orientalis 2, Rossianus 865&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, I:&lt;/hi&gt; Enarratio codicum</title><author><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></author><author><forename>Eugène</forename><surname>Tisserant</surname></author><pubPlace>Città del Vaticano</pubPlace><publisher>In Bybliotheca Vaticana</publisher><date>1935</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:GrebTiss1935Codices</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:GrebTiss1935Codices</note><citedRange unit="page">522</citedRange></bibl>.
                     </note>
                     <ab>
                        በእንተ፡ ተአምራቲሁ፡ ወመንክራቲሁ። <supplied reason="omitted">ለ</supplied>ዘከሠተ፡ ኅቡአቲሁ፡ በትንብልናሁ፡ ለሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ሩፋኤል፡ 
                        ወኮነ፡ ዓቢይ፡ ፍሥሓ፡ ወአዘዘ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ያጸርይዎ፡ ለውእቱ፡ ወርቅ፡ በእሳት፡ እስከ፡ ይትነጠፍ፡ እምርስሕቱ። ወበጊዜሃ፡ ገብሩ፡ ሥዕለ፡ ዓቢየ፡ ዘወርቅ። ንጡፍ፡ 
                        በዓምሳለ፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ሩፋኤል<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied>
                     </ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="MiracleSeaMonster">
                     <label>Miracle of the keeper of a church, who was carried away by a sea monster</label>
                     <note>This miracle is different from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7164MRWhale">Dǝrsāna
                                                  Rufāʾel element div with id LIT7164MRWhale</ref>, where a king is swallowed by a sea monster.
                        The following incipit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet130">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 130</ref> according to <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/QZH8VYBF"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/><title level="m">Bybliothecae apostolicae Vaticanae codices manu scripti recensiti iussu Pii XI Pontificis maximi. Codices Aethiopici Vaticani et Borgiani, Barberinianus orientalis 2, Rossianus 865&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, I:&lt;/hi&gt; Enarratio codicum</title><author><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></author><author><forename>Eugène</forename><surname>Tisserant</surname></author><pubPlace>Città del Vaticano</pubPlace><publisher>In Bybliotheca Vaticana</publisher><date>1935</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:GrebTiss1935Codices</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:GrebTiss1935Codices</note><citedRange unit="page">522</citedRange></bibl>.
                     </note>
                     <ab>
                        <choice><sic>አጠይቀክሙ፡</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">አጤይቀክሙ፡</corr></choice> ኦአኃውየ፡ ዕፁበ፡ ወመንክረ፡ 
                        ካልዓ፡ ዘገብረ፡ ተአምረ፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ጸሎቱ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/> ስምዑ፡ እንግርክሙ፡ ኦጉባኤ፡ ማኅበራ፡ ለቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡
                        ቅድስት፨ ሀሎ፡ ፩ዓቃቤ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ወበአሐቲ፡ ዕለት፡ ቦአ፡ ከመ፡ ያብርህ፡ ማኅቶተ፡ ቅድመ፡ <sic>ሥዕል፡</sic> ክቡር፡ ሩፋኤል<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied>
                     </ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="MiracleConstantine">
                     <label>On how Raphael appeared to emperor Constantine</label>
                     <note>
                        The following incipit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet130">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 130</ref> according to <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/QZH8VYBF"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/><title level="m">Bybliothecae apostolicae Vaticanae codices manu scripti recensiti iussu Pii XI Pontificis maximi. Codices Aethiopici Vaticani et Borgiani, Barberinianus orientalis 2, Rossianus 865&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, I:&lt;/hi&gt; Enarratio codicum</title><author><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></author><author><forename>Eugène</forename><surname>Tisserant</surname></author><pubPlace>Città del Vaticano</pubPlace><publisher>In Bybliotheca Vaticana</publisher><date>1935</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:GrebTiss1935Codices</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:GrebTiss1935Codices</note><citedRange unit="page">523</citedRange></bibl>.
                     </note>
                     <ab>
                        ናሁ፡ ንጽሕፍ፡ ለክሙ፡ ኦአኃውየ፡ ፍቁራን፡ ኃይለ፡ ዘገብረ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ሩፋኤል፡ አመ፡ ተፈነወ፡ ውስተ፡ ቤተ፡ ቈስጠንጢኖስ፡
                        ንጉሥ፡ ዘተመስሎ፡ ለአብርሃም፡ በሠዊዓ፡ ወልዱ፡ ወምንተ፡ ገብረ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መልአክ፡ ሩፋኤል፡ ወሶበ፡ ረከቦ፡ <supplied reason="omitted">ለ</supplied>ንዑሠ፡ 
                        መዋዕል፡ ወልዱ፡ ለቈስጠንጢኖስ፡
                     </ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="MiracleTobias">
                     <label>Miracle of Tobias</label>
                     <note>
                        The following incipit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet130">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 130</ref> according to <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/QZH8VYBF"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/><title level="m">Bybliothecae apostolicae Vaticanae codices manu scripti recensiti iussu Pii XI Pontificis maximi. Codices Aethiopici Vaticani et Borgiani, Barberinianus orientalis 2, Rossianus 865&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, I:&lt;/hi&gt; Enarratio codicum</title><author><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></author><author><forename>Eugène</forename><surname>Tisserant</surname></author><pubPlace>Città del Vaticano</pubPlace><publisher>In Bybliotheca Vaticana</publisher><date>1935</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:GrebTiss1935Codices</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:GrebTiss1935Codices</note><citedRange unit="page">523</citedRange></bibl>.
                     </note>
                     <ab>
                        ሣልስኒ፡ ተአምሪሁ፡ ለዝንቱ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> መልአክ፡ ነበረ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ በዘመነ፡ አበዊነ፡ ቀደምት። 
                        <choice><sic>ዘልሙ</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ዘስሙ፡</corr></choice> ጦቢት፡ ወስመ፡ ወልዱ፡ ጦብያ። ወሠናይ፡ ውእቱ፡ 
                        ብእሲሁ፡ ወያፈቅሮ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፨ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/> ወበእንተ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ተጽሕፈ፡ ምስለ፡ ዜና፡ 
                        መልአክ፡ ሩፋኤል፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ነገሩ፡ ለጦቢት፡ ወልደ፡ ጦብያ፤ ወልደ፡ ገባል፡ ዘእምነ፡ አሳሔል፤ ዘእምነገደ፡ ንፍታሌም፤ 
                     </ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
               
